  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a pilot study of a wearable type of kidney dialysis machine to treat patients with
      chronic kidney disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a pilot study to evaluate the clearances, tolerability and safety of a wearable
      artificial kidney device for treating patients with chronic kidney failure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
